contents.desc: Replying to @crestyy l abandoned my cheating wife after catching her with a famous celebrity. I received a midnight call from her, and with a voice full of excitement, she said she'd be spending the night with an actor she'd just met, thinking I'd be understanding because it was a "once-in-a-lifetime opportunity." She ended the call, leaving me sitting there, shocked. The day she returned home, she was expecting a normal welcome, but instead, she found an empty house, no kids, no sign of me. She thought it was just a fling, but she came back to find her entire life turned upside down. Part3
